Annotation Type XmlNs


  • @Documented
 @Target(value={})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface XmlNs
    Namespace name/URL mapping pair.

    Used to identify a namespace/URI pair on a @XmlSchema(xmlNs) annotation.
